Package main.core.floorsubsystem

Class EventObj

java.lang.Object
main.core.floorsubsystem.EventObj
public class EventObj
extends java.lang.Object
This class provides an implementation of an object meant for storing the details of Elevator system-related events.
Author:
Tony Zeidan, Evan Lloyd, Shaopeng Liu, Leenesh Kumar, YouHeng Zhou, Dominic Motora
